versions.version_description: Includes chords with bass notes, riffs, chord legend, and info on live versions keys.

Classic Elvis Tune in a Modified DADGAD Tuning (CGDGAD) and a Capo clipped at Fret No. 5 which gives this song a much more interesting feel than the boring versions already out there. Please Comment and Rate.
